conbody.p:
The Analytics Administration window also displays the Model Execution metrics table. You can see the following properties:
Model Name—name of the model.
Executed—number of times the model was run.
Succeeded—number of successful runs.
Last success—date and time of the last successful run.
Failures—number of failed runs.
Last Failure—date and time of the last failed run.
Avg.Time—Average run time of the model.
